name: CUBI (MadMath123)
description:
There are so many platformer titles. I bet you could think of a lot right now. Heck, there's a who section for them! But what if we change some of those rules? What if we... change perspective?

In CUBI, you'll be faced with different challenges that push your brain. In this world,  platforming skills won't necessarily serve you well. With 17 levels, it's not very long, but it's fun.
